    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let go of the past\"... i dont know. it feels less like let go and more like there's nothing left to hold onto. it's not just being empty, it's the feeling that the story is already finished. like the credits are rolling but i'm still sitting in the theater. does it ever feel to you like some things are just meant to reach an end?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
