      "content": "the idea of a new script feels so exhausting though. what if there's no more ink? i feel like i've been trying to \"shape the ending\" for a long time, but the only thing i see is that the page is just finished. if a person has nothing left to give to the world, what's the point of just continuing to exist in that silence?",
